{
  "stem": "18486.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 182,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Jewish people in our village, or in the villages, had-- were forced to come to a Jewish part in-- in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 182,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when those friends of ours, who were very famous musicians, when they were ordered to go to Amsterdam, they had a little boy.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 182,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were extremely worried to take the child there, because they didn't know what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 182,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we said, well, give him to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 182,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we took him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 183,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 184,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nap-- N-A-P-- that was his first name-- De-- D-E-- Klyn-- K-L-Y-N.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 184,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was a very famous violinist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 185,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 185,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was a pianist, and her name was Alice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 185,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A-L-I-S-E.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 185,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "C-E.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 186,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mark.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 187,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they stayed-- they left the child with you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 188,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They left the child.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 188,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they also were in hiding, and when there was a difficulty, or a danger, then they came to us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 188,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we lived in the same village where they lived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 188,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so it was too dangerous to have them with us-- for them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 188,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because people who would come to us might recognize them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 188,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they-- were not hidden-- they once in awhile, for a week or so, when there was trouble, they would come to us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 188,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But in general, they were hidden in Amsterdam with other people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 189,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which people, you mean?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 190,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, people who came to our house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 190,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we became very, very careful with who came to our house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 190,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But of course, they had a room upstairs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 190,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- and-- so, sometimes we had people who we didn't know-- want to know that we had Jewish people in the house.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 190,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But our friends and all knew it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 190,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had did this themselves, the same as we did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 191,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Your children knew that there were Jewish--",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
